name: "Hush Hush" by Ted Emmons
description:
Photographer Ted Emmons presents “Youthful Waste”, a collection of
photography that vascillates between stark, minimalist imagery and
vibrantly patterned graphics to paint a picture of modern California
as told through his lens.

A native of Southern California, Emmons accomplished and received
early recognition for his creative and artistic abilities with
published and commissioned mediums in digital and graphic designs,
sculptures and paintings. Emmons continues to push the limits when it
comes to his personal and professional portfolio.

All prints are Limited Edition. 24"x36". Each piece is hand signed and numbered by the artist.
